{"tid":793330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"到底像不像？？ 大胃王作曲家撞臉防彈少年團JIMIN：BTS不能隨便碰","createTime":"2018-08-25T10:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T02:49:04.000Z","uid":193951,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45544fcd3a252ecd5857f4250c419e7ad21260db","tid":793330,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"在韓網上搜過防彈少年團JIMIN關聯詞會跳出「Don Spike」，前者是炙手可熱人氣爆棚的大勢男團成員，後者是作曲家兼大胃王，兩人到底有什麼關係呢？<br />\n<br />\n引起熱議的就是這張照片！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/182509_1ef7b4b9e0305260314cf216b48eed36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F182509_1ef7b4b9e0305260314cf216b48eed36.jpg&h=dd0f3121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論是韓媒還是韓國的粉絲們看到照片後都驚呼「兩人實在是太像了！！！ 」<br />\n<br />\n作為超人氣男團的一員，JIMIN在全球都有粉絲。 而Don Spike除了是作曲家的身份外，大家更熟悉的其實是他大胃王的身份。 尤其是自製的獨家巨型牛排，讓人看了好想啃上一口。 單獨看兩人似乎找不到任何相似點，可是神奇的是一旦把他們的照片放到一起，就莫名感覺神似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/182551_832647b621b6ce4f22b6741f081ca2de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F182551_832647b621b6ce4f22b6741f081ca2de.jpg&h=fa259ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/182554_a4af45fbc28ad473536b2fca836e357e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F182554_a4af45fbc28ad473536b2fca836e357e.jpg&h=1443ae2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDon Spike某檔節目時就被主持人「聽說最近你的外貌和某一超人氣愛豆很像，是嗎？ 」Don Spike聽到問題後立刻作出了回應，並說道：<span style=\"color: red;\">「請別再說下去了，因為這個問題，我本人已經受到了不少人身攻擊。 」</span>隨後主持人還表示如果稍微瘦點的話，還真的很像。 但是對此，Don Spike仍然堅決否認，並稱絕對不一樣，並再一次表示不願意承認。 最後他說到：<span style=\"color: red;\">「防彈少年團不能隨便碰，如果因此惹怒了ARMY，會出大事情的。 哈哈。 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/182626_f160b5cc812e6e44a58f0c686ca026e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F182626_f160b5cc812e6e44a58f0c686ca026e4.jpg&h=a07fd8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/182629_c1e3dc3a7b282e7e441387a70d51cf4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F182629_c1e3dc3a7b282e7e441387a70d51cf4e.jpg&h=98fbc9b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca328dad55b23bb35778b4ead8d217700552fdcd","tid":793330,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"好似大陸民工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c86a4aed1ea1ddd1d1321cea062839702780e","tid":793330,"uid":21398,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"光頭王靚仔D"},{"pid":"bded3def705fd479c982af89dc4d06bbbed3f784","tid":793330,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係幾柒下"},{"pid":"b21d6e4a74f84d99d83264002d460a9a43c39a57","tid":793330,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bded3def705fd479c982af89dc4d06bbbed3f784","tid":793330,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係幾柒下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"邊個?"},{"pid":"fa06449c9c25714577e2e653531f4ce7d96b43c5","tid":793330,"uid":555,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b21d6e4a74f84d99d83264002d460a9a43c39a57","tid":793330,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bded3def705fd479c982af89dc4d06bbbed3f784","tid":793330,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係幾柒下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"邊個?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"jimin"},{"pid":"a2bf67104202501bf9b5b3240c06d0510f81cb3c"